title: LTS - Celtic Core / Intime Ocean
description:
Two albums by LTS - a French instrumental Celtic punk band from the turn of the millennium. It was pretty obscure even back then so I thought why not put this up on torrents. Production/encoding quality is not exactly fit for audiophiles, especially Celtic Core, but you won't find any better. If you like Celtic tunes combined with heavy guitar riffs, you'll probably like LTS.
